Hello, Dr. Sturgis.
This is Mary Cooper.

8
00:00:13,399 --> 00:00:17,188
Did you know there's a, uh,
supercollider being built

9
00:00:17,273 --> 00:00:19,429
- in Waxahachie, Texas?
