That's a great question.

14
00:00:28,531 --> 00:00:29,875
No.

15
00:00:32,745 --> 00:00:34,657
JEFF: Since everyone is going
back to school tomorrow,

16
00:00:34,741 --> 00:00:37,281
let's finish up
with a back-to-school prayer.

17
00:00:37,365 --> 00:00:38,470
What?

18
00:00:38,554 --> 00:00:40,314
Does this prayer just
apply to middle school,

19
00:00:40,398 --> 00:00:42,773
