for the college-bound?

20
00:00:42,858 --> 00:00:44,167
It's for everyone.

21
00:00:44,252 --> 00:00:46,766
But thank you once again
for reminding us

22
00:00:46,851 --> 00:00:47,958
you're starting college.

23
00:00:48,042 --> 00:00:50,085
Oh, I don't mind.
You've got a lot on your plate.

24
00:00:50,182 --> 00:00:51,466
Just pray.

25
00:00:51,890 --> 00:00:55,157
ALL: Dear Heavenly Father,
as we return to school,

26
00:00:55,242 --> 00:00:56,421
we look to your eternal...

27
00:00:56,506 --> 00:00:57,966
Billy, it's not the pledge.

28
00:01:01,017 --> 00:01:03,277
<i>It is clear that we cannot
expect the cooperation...</i> - [phone ringing]

29
